  ('optometrist-moex-03578', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '一位病患戴+9.00 DS的一般眼鏡，頂點距離為12.0 mm，因為最近鼻子開刀，需要將頂點距離調整到22 mm， 則此時需要將眼鏡調整為何？', '["+7.25 DS", "+8.25 DS", "+9.25 DS", "+10.25 DS"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c0506c210b76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f66fae525935", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106111", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 47, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03579', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於Purkinje影像之敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["Purkinje影像II比Purkinje影像Ⅰ距角膜頂點遠", "Purkinje影像II會產生正像及虛像", "Purkinje影像III是水晶體前表面所產生的", "Purkinje影像IV會產生實像及倒像"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c0506c210b76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f66fae525935", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106111", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 48, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
