  ('optometrist-moex-03581', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '患者的處方是右眼+5.00DS/-1.00DC×090，1ΔBI（基底朝內）、左眼+3.00DS/-1.00DC×090，1ΔBI（基底 朝內）、瞳孔間距右眼32 mm，左眼31 mm、鏡框瞳孔間距70 mm，右眼與左眼各須從光學中心移多少 mm就可得1ΔBI（基底朝內）稜鏡效應？', '["右眼5.5 mm往內；左眼7.3 mm往內", "右眼5.5 mm往內；左眼7.3 mm往外", "右眼5.5 mm往外；左眼7.3 mm往內", "右眼5.5 mm往外；左眼7.3 mm往外"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "c0506c210b76", "answer_pdf_sha1": "f66fae525935", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106111", "c": "112", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年第二次專技人員高等考試中醫師考試分階段考試、營養師、心理師、護理師、社會工作師考試、106年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力...", "original_question_number": 50, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('optometrist-moex-03582', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-106-ddcf1380', 'sub-optometrist-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '用一個-3.00 D（diopter）的凹透鏡片看一個直徑40 cm的圓形時鐘，若放在距離時鐘1 m處，則看到的時 鐘直徑大小為何？', '["5 cm", "10 cm", "15 cm", "20 cm"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:56+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "fb0b0bc8f8ae", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5b57eb0a441a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106060", "c": "401", "s": "0802", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "視覺光學", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 1, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL),
